\end_inset

, who found evidence of antagonistic pleiotropy at ten regions across the
 genome using data on both survival and fecundity from the same experiments.
 The discrepancy is likley to be due to QTL for freezing tolerance that
 increase survival in Sweden, but carry a substantial cost in Italy 
